  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Great Demon King wants to conquer this beautiful land. Warriors, assemble your team and repel it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras/458428fd22140aa73e26793aa3018eed.avif?t=1733837479\" width=616 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can choose the Imperial warriors who can evolve up to 5 times!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras/4f4f028aa09f1a27014c989527fb25b0.avif?t=1733837479\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras_big/4f4f028aa09f1a27014c989527fb25b0.avif?t=1733837479 width=800 height=1074 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also choose the wolf pack! By raising werewolves, you can have more and more wolves in your chess pool. Then, by utilizing the synergy effects of the wolf race, you can achieve astonishing combat power to crush your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are also mages here who cast magic missiles like crazy! Are you ready to welcome the feast of magic missiles flying in the sky?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras/89fcb4783001fdf8e112a934ad52bab1.avif?t=1733837479\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras_big/89fcb4783001fdf8e112a934ad52bab1.avif?t=1733837479 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >350+ unique and distinctive chess pieces</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >130+ various treasures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ items that can be used on chess pieces</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 heroes with different styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 maps</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras/71c559f88ba3ba9fb0caac92e3fe6e09.avif?t=1733837479\" width=616 height=164 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Great Demon King wants to conquer this beautiful land. Warriors, assemble your team and repel it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras/458428fd22140aa73e26793aa3018eed.avif?t=1733837479\" width=616 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can choose the Imperial warriors who can evolve up to 5 times!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras/4f4f028aa09f1a27014c989527fb25b0.avif?t=1733837479\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras_big/4f4f028aa09f1a27014c989527fb25b0.avif?t=1733837479 width=800 height=1074 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also choose the wolf pack! By raising werewolves, you can have more and more wolves in your chess pool. Then, by utilizing the synergy effects of the wolf race, you can achieve astonishing combat power to crush your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are also mages here who cast magic missiles like crazy! Are you ready to welcome the feast of magic missiles flying in the sky?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras/89fcb4783001fdf8e112a934ad52bab1.avif?t=1733837479\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras_big/89fcb4783001fdf8e112a934ad52bab1.avif?t=1733837479 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >350+ unique and distinctive chess pieces</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >130+ various treasures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ items that can be used on chess pieces</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 heroes with different styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 maps</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017170/extras/71c559f88ba3ba9fb0caac92e3fe6e09.avif?t=1733837479\" width=616 height=164 /></span></p>",
